<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    He was persuaded/forced to defect as Smiley threatened to expose the use of state funds, personnel and resources to keep his daughter in a Western ins<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    He was persuaded/forced to defect as Smiley threatened to expose the use of state funds, personnel and resources to keep his daughter in a Western institution. Karla/Jean-Luc Pickard (!) crosses the bridge, and then we presume is taken away for an extensive debriefing. Once the UK/US are through with him, we assume he is allowed to resettle somewhere with his daughter.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
