        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2211749835" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2643411328212795371">This is probably the most fulfilling of the Smiley stories. But it does follow the usual format.<br/>Something happens. Smiley is pulled out of retirement. He talks to his old contacts/colleagues. He reads a lot of files. There are lots of words as the story rolls slowly along. Then in the last 20 pages the denouement occurs where the final act is not known till the last page. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


